<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Application Update — TektonX</title>
  <style>
    body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background: #f4f4f5; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; }
    .wrapper { max-width: 560px; margin: 40px auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.12); }
    .header { background: #0f172a; padding: 32px 40px; text-align: center; }
    .header h1 { color: #f8fafc; margin: 0; font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: -0.5px; }
    .header span { color: #7c3aed; }
    .body { padding: 40px; }
    .body h2 { color: #0f172a; margin-top: 0; font-size: 20px; }
    .body p { color: #475569; line-height: 1.6; margin: 12px 0; }
    .reason-box { background: #fef2f2; border-left: 4px solid #fca5a5; padding: 12px 16px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 16px 0; color: #7f1d1d; font-size: 14px; }
    .footer { padding: 20px 40px; background: #f8fafc; text-align: center; }
    .footer p { color: #94a3b8; font-size: 12px; margin: 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Tekton<span>X</span></h1>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <h2>Hi {{name}},</h2>
      <p>Thank you for your interest in becoming a TektonX mentor. After careful review, we're unable to approve your application at this time.</p>
      {{#if reason}}
      <div class="reason-box">
        <strong>Reason:</strong> {{reason}}
      </div>
      {{/if}}
      <p>We appreciate the time you took to apply and encourage you to re-apply in the future as our program grows. If you have any questions, please reach out to us at <a href="mailto:{{contactEmail}}" style="color:#0ea5e9;">{{contactEmail}}</a>.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{year}} TektonX Labs. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
